metadata.name: In the Cathedral with Bach
metadata.description:
360 Musical ImageSphere with original art by SphericalArt and the music of Bach's Orchestral Suite no.3 provided by https://freesfx.co.uk 

Strains of Bach set to SphericalArt's luminous, stainedglass-like geometry in this unique and interactive 360 Musical Imagesphere.

It's the first of its kind from the team called SAID, SphericalArt and Indefatigable. Edition One of One, 8192 x 4096 pixels.Created in 2021.
